<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>يَكُفُّ دَمْعًا كُلَّمَا مُرِي هَمَلْ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>يَغُلُّ فِي لِحْيَتِهِ أَيَّ غَلَلْ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>أي <span class="c1">"مُرِيَ"</span> اسْتُدِرَّ واسْتُخْرِجَ،<span class="c5"> ومثله:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَيْحَكِ أُمَّ الوَرْدِ هَنْكِ الفَلْهَمُ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>يَضِلُّ فِيهِ الصَّمَيَانُ المِقْلَمُ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>أي هَنُكِ،<span class="c5"> ومثله:</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَأَنْتِ لَوْ صَبَّحْتِ مَشْمُولَةً ... صَهْبَاءَ مِثْلَ الفَرَسِ الأَشْقَرِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>رُحْتِ وَفِي الرِّجْلَيْنِ مَا فِيهِمَا ... وَقَدْ بَدَا هَنْكِ مِنَ المِئْزَرِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">ومثله:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>لمَّا رَأَى أَنْ لَا دَعَهْ وَلَا شَبَعْ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>مالَ إلَى أَرْطَاةِ حِقْفٍ فَاضْطَجَعْ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>فجزم <span class="c1">"أَنْ لَا دَعَةَ"</span>،<span class="c5"> ومثله:</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>